OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fclear spells for most overnight.
OL,7,FHowever, low cloud near eastern coasts
OL,8,Fwill redevelop and extend into many
OL,9,Fcentral areas by dawn. A warm night in
OL,10,Fthe south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAreas of cloud across eastern
OL,13,Fcounties receding, but lingering near
OL,14,FNorth Sea coasts. Otherwise, a dry day
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells. Another very warm
OL,16,Fday, locally hot in the southwest.
